top to bottom direction
hide empty description
title UEORMS State Transition - 3) Workflow, Audit, and Notifications

[*] --> WorkflowConfigured
WorkflowConfigured --> RequestSubmitted : submit request
RequestSubmitted --> PendingApproval : route approval
PendingApproval --> Approved : approve
PendingApproval --> Rejected : reject
Rejected --> RequestSubmitted : resubmit
Approved --> AuditLogged : audit event
Rejected --> AuditLogged : audit event
AuditLogged --> NotificationQueued : enqueue notices
NotificationQueued --> NotificationDelivered : delivered
NotificationDelivered --> NotificationRead : mark read
NotificationDelivered --> RealtimeStreamed : realtime push
RealtimeStreamed --> NotificationRead
NotificationRead --> [*]

@enduml
